---
import Icon from "astro-icon";
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-3" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, I'm Michael Kurniawan, a Software Engineer from Indonesia.
      <br>
      My primary skills includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li role="link">JavaScript</li>
        <li role="link">PHP</li>
        <li role="link">Laravel</li>
        <li role="link">Flutter</li>
        <li role="link">Kotlin</li>
        <li role="link">Go</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about product design and human behavior and business management.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
